metadata.name: All Eyes R on U
metadata.description:
This image is a digital representation of the one of my physical acrylic paintings on canvas from 2016.

He is trying to isolate himself in the deep space of his mind to listen to his inner voice. But, still can not escape from the eyes that constantly watching him. 

Whoever buys this digital version of my artwork will also have the original one. 

Canvas size 50cm x 60cm

Digital Image 3024px x 2530px
